.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH wsp-repo 1  "repo " 
.SH NAME
repo \- Manage repos in the current workspace
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBrepo\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage repos in the current workspace
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
repo\-add(1)
Add repos to current workspace
.TP
repo\-rm(1)
Remove repo(s) from the current workspace
.TP
repo\-fetch(1)
Fetch updates for workspace repos
.TP
repo\-ls(1)
List repos in the current workspace [read\-only]
.TP
repo\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
